OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny remaining showers will soon
OL,6,Fclear east, leaving a dry and very
OL,7,Fwarm day with plenty of hazy sunshine.
OL,8,FLight winds will do little to
OL,9,Falleviate the heat.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry, mostly clear but humid
OL,12,Fnight is expected with light winds.
OL,13,FSome patchy mist may form inland and
OL,14,Falong the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FDry with long sunny periods
OL,17,Fand light winds. Widely very warm or
OL,18,Fhot, including overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
