OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMostly dry with long sunny periods,
OL,7,Fthough thundery showers may develop on
OL,8,FFriday. Widely very warm, including
OL,9,Fovernight. Less hot on Saturday with
OL,10,Fmore cloud and showers over the hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
